thread.title: Carroll rolls by Boone, 34 – 14

author: KWBG
title: Carroll rolls by Boone, 34 – 14
text:
Carroll rolls by Boone, 34 – 14 Posted on 02 October 2015 by KWBG 
At Goeppinger Field Friday night, Boone spotted Carroll 21 first-half points before the Toreadors’ Kaden Sherrard had a 7-yard touchdown at the end of the first half. However, a 1-yard t-d dive by quarterback Tanner Schminke at the end of the game was the only other score Boone could manage as the Tigers roared to a 34 – 14 victory. With that homecoming loss, the Toreadors fall to 1 and 4 on the year, but remain in Boone next week against Algona, who pounded Perry, 52 – 14. Leave a Reply You must be logged in to post a comment. Boone Municipal, IA
